data.description: This is a desirable property. Offering convenient access with no steps, with all new carpet throughout, and freshly painted located in a quiet neighborhood with little traffic and assigned parking. Crofton, MD is known as a wonderful town. Located in one of the best counties for education in America. This house is an attractive location for new families and includes community pools and playgrounds.  Also, it is a wonderful property for independent seniors. Being centrally located in the Washington DC metro, Baltimore, and the Bay Bridge also adds to its appeal.  Convenient shopping, restaurants, and close to Arundel Mills, Bowie Town Center, and Wegman's supermarket. If you are looking for a low to no maintenance living this is the property for you.  The price has been reduced by $29,500.00. No contingencies  If you are interested in the property, DONT LET THIS ONE GET AWAY.........
